<p>科琳是英国着名球星鲁尼的爱妻，两人婚后一共育有四个孩子。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200905/3bdf75143edb4684a1088769a6df6a0a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
